  storyText: "Well, my family is quite small, or at least I think it is. I am the
    eldest of the family, though I do have 1 younger sister, for better or worse.{wc}Ah,
    that reminds me, I hope my parents can manage her without me\u2026 my she can
    be quite the little annoying devil, trust me."
