  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 125
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Sadly, I haven\u2019t managed to move out of my parent\u2019s home
    yet. Too much money for such a small place\u2026 truly, we live in terrible times.{wc}If
    I could, though, you\u2019d know I\u2019d be right out the door and sprinting
    towards the nearest rentable place, haha!"
