  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 132
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "You must know that I want to get my bio-medical sciences degree and
    get into med school, yes?{wc}Then you also must know that I want to be an apothecary
    of sorts, and that I\u2019m currently working towards getting my \u201Cdream
    job\u201D too! Honestly, you need to pay more attention to what I say!"
