  storyText: "Yes, actually! I saw an advertisement for a very nice looking buffet
    just a few streets down from here, so naturally I had to go check it out!{wc}It
    was very nice there, though their prices were surprisingly cheap for a plate
    of ham they serve there, but I won\u2019t complain about saving some money on
    my favorite food!"
