  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ec422cd568a9c4a31ad7c36d0572b9da, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemId: 129
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: "Well, I don\u2019t really have a \u201Cfavorite food\u201D! The concept
    of having only one thing that you always eat no matter what was always a bit
    silly to me, honestly.{wc}You would always eat that food? What if you get sick
    of it one day? What if the brand you buy disappears from the store one day?{wc}I\u2019d
    rather eat a bunch of foods and like them than tie myself to one specific food."
  description: 
