  itemId: 128
  indentLevel: 0
  storyText: 'What an interesting question! Well, I quite like the humble scarab,
    but any of the other beetles in their family are nice too.{wc}I specifically
    am quite fond of the rainbow scarab beetle, mainly because of its colors, but
    if I had the option of reincarnating into any regular scarab beetle I would also
    do so!

'
